title: Prince Royce: What's Your Favorite Collab From New Album 'Five'? Vote! | Billboard
text:
COMMENTS Taylor Hill/FilmMagic Prince Royce performs during Mega 96.3's Calibash 2017 at Staples Center on Jan. 21, 2017 in Los Angeles. 
The day has finally arrived! Prince Royce 's new album Five dropped Friday (Feb. 24), featuring collabs with superstars like Shakira , Farruko , Chris Brown and Zendaya . 
From Royce's tropical, urban song "Ganas locas" featuring Farru to the bachata tune "Deja vu" featuring Shakira and "X" with Zendaya, there are lots of team-ups to choose from. 
Prince Royce fans, this is your chance to make your voice heard and vote for your favorite collab on the album:
